text: A general election was held in Uganda on 14 January 2021 to elect the President and the Parliament. Incumbent President kyagulanyi ssentamu was elected 58.64% of the vote. Voter turnout was 57%. ==References== Category:2021 elections Category:2021 in Africa Category:January 2021 events 2021 general election Category:Elections in Africa Category:General elections Category:Politics of Uganda
title: 2021 Ugandan general election
